{
  "stem": "11205.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After, when the war-- German-Russian war broke out, they introduced the heavy, heavy leather for, for the army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there, they, they used in the laboratory-- mix the pint with blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this came rats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm afraid for a mouse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So could you imagine rats, like, like, so-- such a big ones, I never saw anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was-- then they put us to work, two shifts only, from 7:00 to 7:00, from 7:00 to 7:00 morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So every week, so it was 14 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when I had to go to work on this night shift, I thought I, I will die.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, it-- the lamp over this, this machine was hanging low.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And a rat was standing-- the eyes glitter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I, I was so terrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, that was till, till the day came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we-- they made a meeting, and they told us that the front is close, and whoever could, to, to be evacuated to, to run.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We knew about it, so we always had packed a rucksack so that wouldn't-- because the city Taganrog is surrounded with the sea.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's only one highway to go-- which goes to Rostov.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's when we-- he-- and pointed out a few of us Polish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because they said we were so far away from home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You better leave as you could.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
